1
00:00:26,910 --> 00:00:28,310
Prajem ti príjemný let.

2
00:00:31,710 --> 00:00:35,710
Dávaj si na seba pozor.

3
00:00:40,440 --> 00:00:41,930
Maj sa, Tum.

4
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:47,040
Ahoj.

5
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:48,640
Tum.

6
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:12,570
Na zdravie!

7
00:02:17,950 --> 00:02:19,000
Hotovo!

8
00:02:21,660 --> 00:02:22,570
Čo si urobil?

9
00:02:22,570 --> 00:02:23,570
Čo?

10
00:02:24,130 --> 00:02:25,280
Nič.

11
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,240
Kto prehral?

12
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:38,200
Hej.

13
00:03:38,530 --> 00:03:39,710
Hej!

14
00:03:39,710 --> 00:03:40,570
Hej...

15
00:03:40,570 --> 00:03:42,570
- Daj mi dva!
- Choď.

16
00:03:42,570 --> 00:03:45,710
- Poďme.
- Poďme.

17
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,020
Toto je dobré miesto.

18
00:03:53,950 --> 00:03:55,310
Tu!

19
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,400
- Zapaľovač.
- Aj ja ho mám.

20
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,750
Odkiaľ ho máš?

21
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,840
Ae, nepridáš sa k nám?

22
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,440
Nie, budem sa iba pozerať.

23
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:05,150
Ako chceš...

24
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:07,150
Bože, fúka vietor.

25
00:04:10,110 --> 00:04:13,880
No tak, urob mi clonu.

26
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,650
Ahoj.

27
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:24,270
Pete!

28
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,180
Zapni si videohovor.

29
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,820
Ae?

30
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:41,480
Vždy keď ťa vidím,
tak mi strašne chýbaš.

31
00:04:41,820 --> 00:04:43,660
Ale som rád, že tu nie si.

32
00:04:43,660 --> 00:04:45,130
Prečo?

33
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:48,240
Dobre ma počúvaj.

34
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,240
Som rád, že tu nie si, 

35
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:53,170
pretože keby si tu bol,
tak by sme nevyšli z hotelovej izby.

36
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:56,820
Pred minútou sme si spievali ľúbostné pesničky.

37
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,590
Začal som pri nich myslieť na teba.

38
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:02,420
Aj ty si spieval?

39
00:05:02,730 --> 00:05:04,240
Nie som v tom dobrý.

40
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:06,240
Väčšinu pesničiek si už nepamätám.

41
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:10,860
Mohol by si mi niečo zaspievať?

42
00:05:12,970 --> 00:05:15,440
Veď som ti povedal,
že neviem spievať.

43
00:05:19,860 --> 00:05:24,910
Dobre, tak ti jednu zaspievam.

44
00:05:25,820 --> 00:05:27,310
Akú pesničku?

45
00:05:31,170 --> 00:05:33,020
Nie, zmenil som názor.

46
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:35,080
Nechcem, aby si počul moje kvílenie.

47
00:05:36,170 --> 00:05:37,990
No tak, zaspievaj mi niečo.

48
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,260
Prosím...

49
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,110
Prosím...

50
00:05:42,590 --> 00:05:44,020
Dobre.

51
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:47,060
Zaspievam to iba raz,
tak ma dobre počúvaj.

52
00:05:47,130 --> 00:05:48,020
Dobre.

53
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,970
<i>- Som odvážny stáť tu pri tebe -</i>

54
00:05:53,970 --> 00:05:59,420
<i>- a to všetko vďaka láske -</i>

55
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,680
<i>- Viem sa pri tebe vždy uvoľniť -</i>

56
00:06:01,730 --> 00:06:06,990
<i>- a to všetko vďaka láske -</i>

57
00:06:06,990 --> 00:06:10,620
<i>- Možno nemám žiadnu šancu byť s tebou-</i>

58
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:14,260
<i>- no keby som ťa nemiloval,
neskôr by som to oľutoval -</i>

59
00:06:14,330 --> 00:06:17,190
<i>- Som ochotný počkať -</i>

60
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:20,620
<i>- Si môj cieľ, ale aj odmena -</i>

61
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:25,260
<i>- Budem ti hovoriť, ako ťa milujem, -</i>

62
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:29,930
<i>- pokým moju lásku neprijmeš -</i>

63
00:06:30,710 --> 00:06:32,640
Mal by som s tým prestať...

64
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,640
Spievam falošne.

65
00:06:36,420 --> 00:06:37,620
Ae.

66
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:40,130
Milujem ťa.

67
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,440
Nemusíš mi to hovoriť, 

68
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,950
pretože už to dávno viem.

69
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,640
Už som ti to povedal?

70
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:53,950
Si moja prvá láska.

71
00:06:59,150 --> 00:07:00,620
A už som ti to povedal?

72
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,640
Milujem ťa, Pete.

73
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:41,170
Ďakujem.

74
